  "exam_tips": [
    "Domain 2 (Vault Administration) carries the most weight — know safe permissions deeply",
    "PSM session recording is frequently tested — know the configuration steps",
    "CPM credential rotation troubleshooting is a common exam topic",
    "Know the difference between CPM, PSM and PVWA — what each component does",
    "Dual control workflow is tested in both PSM and PVWA domains",
    "Understand the Master Policy and how it interacts with platform policies",
    "Know what happens when CPM fails to rotate a password",
    "Break glass accounts are tested — know when and how to use them"
  ],
